arameter's estimator to explore the quality of different generators. This procedure, easily computable, allows us to extract an efficient method of simulation. In the Appendix are described the S-plus scripts related to simulation and identification methods of the fBm","documentType":"","doi":"10.18637/jss.v005.i07","downloadUrl":"https://www.jstatsoft.org/index.php/jss/article/view/v005i07/622","fieldOfStudy":"article","fullText":"Not available for public API users.","id":28568172,"identifiers":[{"identifier":"26432870","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"oai:doaj.org/article:89d7a3fbb75144d4885417f49ef1508d","type":"oai_id"},{"identifier":"52003366","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"10.18637/jss.v005.i07","type":"doi"},{"identifier":"oai:hal:hal-00383120v1","type":"oai_id"},{"identifier":"90399386","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"oai:doaj.org/article:1887b7e818a44275a891a392e1d8b30a","type":"oai_id"},{"identifier":"102309332","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"oai:citeseerx.psu:10.1.1.614.3931","type":"oai_id"},{"identifier":"206207921","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"478955141","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"oai:ojs.pkp.sfu.ca:article/2018","type":"oai_id"},{"identifier":"625898742","type":"core_id"},{"identifier":"oai:doaj.org/article:89d7a3fbb75144d4885417f49ef1508d","type":"oai"},{"identifier":"oai:hal:hal-00383120v1","type":"oai"},{"identifier":"oai:doaj.org/article:1887b7e818a44275a891a392e1d8b30a","type":"oai"},{"identifier":"oai:citeseerx.psu:10.1.1.614.3931","type":"oai"},{"identifier":"oai:ojs.pkp.sfu.ca:article/2018","type":"oai"}],"title":"Simulation and identification of the fractional Brownian motion: a bibliographical and comparative study","language":{"code":"en","name":"English"},"magId":null,"oaiIds":["oai:doaj.org/article:89d7a3fbb75144d4885417f49ef1508d","oai:hal:hal-00383120v1","oai:doaj.org/article:1887b7e818a44275a891a392e1d8b30a","oai:citeseerx.psu:10.1.1.614.3931","oai:ojs.pkp.sfu.ca:article/2018"],"publishedDate":"2000-01-01T00:00:00+00:00"